msgid "Limit Registration Domain"
msgstr ""

#: domain-restricted-registration.php:151
msgid "If set, only email addresses from this domain may register and new accounts must confirm their email before logging in. Leave empty to allow all domains. Requires \"Anyone can register\" to be enabled above."
msgstr ""

